            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Silvano <lb n="2"/>Domesti<lb break="no" n="3"/>co <expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Taurinus <lb n="5"/>optio <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>XIIII <expan><abbr>gem</abbr><ex>inae</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>Anton</abbr><ex>inianae</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar oder Basis. Zeile 6-8 stark beschädigt und nur noch schwer lesbar. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Auf der linken Nebenseite Patera, auf der rechten Nebenseite Opferkanne.</p>
            </div>
